{"tid":926151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[報應] 3歲女童沙田海關宿舍猝死　母親撫屍哭別女兒","createTime":"2018-12-03T08:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T11:15:36.000Z","uid":224066,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a72f32a89595efc34b067d20371384cfbd0775c","tid":926151,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"沙田康林苑海泓閣海關宿舍，今早(3日)9時許，一名3歲女童被父親發現昏迷在單位內，慌忙報警求助，救護員接報到場，證實女童已氣絕身亡。警方正展開調查，據悉，女童本身有患病紀錄，惟死因有待剖驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181203/photo/bkn-20181203100012504-1203_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181203163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181203100012504-1203_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181203163054&h=a479d2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至下午2時許，女童的遺體由仵工舁走，其母親手抱一名小童，在丈夫及一名年長親友陪同下，傷心送別女兒最後一程，期間，母親難捨女兒，一度撫屍痛哭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181203/photo/bkn-20181203100012504-1203_00822_001_06b.jpg?20181203163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181203100012504-1203_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20181203163054&h=219b1954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公墓園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56b375f315cd0313ecfdf77ccaea390777e13c9","tid":926151,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"明明刷到唔錯既局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜。"},{"pid":"22f7752cbddf87f27f710267b7fd57ea5e7cc6e1","tid":926151,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"is that karma?"}]}